short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This chrome extension fills out forms automatically.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This plugin is created for use with Alphaseq security box (ASB). This plugin automatically fills in credentials of any website by searching and taking inputs from ASB through unencrypted or encrypted communication.
